      <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:26;193:10" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/specialization-domains-attribute.dita">Note that the value for the <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:22;193:46" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/specialization-domains-attribute.dita">domains</xmlatt> attribute is not authored; Instead,
